CuteAdmin
=========

Generator of simple administration, much better than scaffold.
Pagination, ordering, search and i18n support included.

Very *experimental* version for Rails edge (2.2).


Installation:

git clone git://github.com/jana4u/cute_admin.git


Required plugins:

* git://github.com/clemens/localized_dates.git
* git://github.com/iain/i18n_label.git
* git://github.com/binarylogic/searchgasm.git


Usage:

1. generate models
2. run `rake db:migrate`
3. set associations
4. set acts_as_cute_admin.
5. run `./script/generate cute_admin Developer --add-associated`


Example
=======

class Country < ActiveRecord::Base
  acts_as_cute_admin
  has_many :companies
end

class Company < ActiveRecord::Base
  acts_as_cute_admin
  belongs_to :country
  has_many :developers
end

class Developer < ActiveRecord::Base
  acts_as_cute_admin :display_name => :full_name, :order_by => [:last_name, :first_name]
  belongs_to :company

  def full_name
    "#{last_name}, #{first_name}"
  end
end

